Kodi Search / Recommendations for Android TV
--------------------------------------------






Ideas for Recommendations:
##########################


Movies:

Ideas:
Check last 15 movies, get main actors, directors, roles...

Then find:
- unwatched movies with high rating
- newer movies better than older
- search for same directors
- search for same actors
- search for same genre
- randomness
- recently aborted videos
- brand new movies
- files from set
- movies with roles that also appear in other movies
- based on previous searches?


Series:

- started series (next episodes) / new series when old series finished
- incomplete episodes
- genre
- actors